 {\"sentence\": \"She desperately went on her phone to fill out the online form to get her QR code, unaware that the vetting process could take several days.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her phone\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"the online form\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"her QR code\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"the vetting process\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"several days\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those with the precious code - either on their phones or printed out on pieces of paper - passed smoothly past police checkpoints at gaps in the barriers taller than most people.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the precious code\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"their phones\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"pieces\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"police checkpoints\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"gaps\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"the barriers\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"most people\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those without got mostly turned away - with no amount of grumbling and cajoling making officers budge.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no amount\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"officers\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's too much, that's over the top, that whole thing is a pain,\\\" grumbled Nassim Bennamou, a delivery man who was denied access to the street leading to Notre Dame Cathedral on his scooter.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"that whole thing\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"a pain\", \"from\